stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Untrained : system start

    Untrained --> Training : admin triggers training (fine-tune)

    Training --> Trained : training completes
    Training --> Failed : error during training
    Failed --> Training : retry training

    Trained --> Saved : save versioned model dir
    Saved --> Active : load latest (singleton)

    Active --> Predicting : analyze request
    Predicting --> Active : return result

    Active --> Training : retrain triggered
